<div class="animate__animated animate__fadeIn">
    <h4 class="text-primary fw-bold mb-4">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-user-pen me-2"></i> Paso 1: Datos del Solicitante
    </h4>

    <div class="row g-4">
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <label class="form-label fw-bold text-muted small">TIPO DE SOLICITANTE</label>
            <select id="SolicitorType" class="form-select form-select-lg rounded-pill border-2" onchange="toggleSolicitorType()">
                <option value="Titular">Titular (El mismo afiliado)</option>
                <option value="Familiar">Familiar Directo</option>
                <option value="TerceroPolicial">Tercero Policial (Efectivo PNP)</option>
                <option value="Tercero">Tercero / Otro (Civil)</option>
            </select>
            <div id="typeHelper" class="form-text mt-2 text-primary">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info me-1"></i> El solicitante es el titular del beneficio.
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-4">
            <label class="form-label fw-bold text-muted small">DNI SOLICITANTE</label>
            <div class="input-group">
                <input type="text" id="SolicitorDni" class="form-control form-control-lg border-2 rounded-start-pill shadow-none" maxlength="8" onkeypress="return isNumber(event)">
                <button class="btn btn-primary px-4 rounded-end-pill shadow-none" type="button" id="btnLupaSolicitor" onclick="openSearchAffiliate('Solicitor')">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass"></i>
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-4">
            <label class="form-label fw-bold text-muted small">CIP SOLICITANTE</label>
            <input type="text" id="SolicitorCip" class="form-control form-control-lg border-2 rounded-pill bg-light" placeholder="N° CIP" readonly>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-4">
            <label class="form-label fw-bold text-muted small">APELLIDOS Y NOMBRES SOLICITANTE</label>
            <input type="text" id="SolicitorName" class="form-control form-control-lg border-2 rounded-pill bg-light" placeholder="Nombres..." readonly>
        </div>

        <div id="sectionAffiliateData" class="col-md-12 d-none">
            <div class="p-4 border-2 border-primary border-dashed rounded-4" style="background-color: rgba(13, 110, 253, 0.05);">
                <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3">
                    <div class="bg-primary text-white rounded-circle d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center me-2" style="width: 30px; height: 30px;">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-link small"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h6 class="text-primary fw-bold mb-0">Vincular a Afiliado Titular (Obligatorio)</h6>
                </div>

                <p class="text-muted small mb-3">
                    Como el solicitante no es el titular, debe buscar y seleccionar al afiliado al que pertenece el beneficio.
                </p>

                <div class="row g-3">
                    <div class="col-md-4">
                        <label class="form-label fw-bold text-muted small">DNI AFILIADO</label>
                        <div class="input-group">
                            <input type="text" id="AffiliateDni" class="form-control border-2 rounded-start-pill bg-white" placeholder="Buscar titular..." readonly>
                            <button class="btn btn-primary rounded-end-pill" type="button" onclick="openSearchAffiliate('Affiliate')">
                                <i class="fa-solid fa-search"></i>
                            </button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-3">
                        <label class="form-label fw-bold text-muted small">CIP AFILIADO</label>
                        <input type="text" id="AffiliateCip" class="form-control border-2 rounded-pill bg-light" readonly>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-5">
                        <label class="form-label fw-bold text-muted small">NOMBRES Y APELLIDOS DEL TITULAR</label>
                        <input type="text" id="AffiliateName" class="form-control border-2 rounded-pill bg-light" readonly>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="d-flex justify-content-end mt-5">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg rounded-pill px-5 shadow"
                onclick="if(validateStep1()) loadStep(2)">
            Siguiente <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right ms-2"></i>
        </button>
    </div>
</div>